org.glassfish.gmbal.impl
Class AMXClient

java.lang.Object
  org.glassfish.gmbal.impl.AMXClient
All Implemented Interfaces:
AMX
public class AMXClient
extends java.lang.Object
implements AMX

This class implements a generic AMX MBean which is connected to a possibly remote MBeanServerConnection (note that MBeanServer isA MBeanServerConnection, so we can actually create an AMXClientImpl simply by using the MBeanServer from the mom: this is useful for testing).

Note that this version of the AMX API provides a generic get/set API that is identical to DynamicMBean, except that it only throws unchecked exceptions. This is far more convenient in practice than the JMX-standard checked exceptions.
